{"tid":2424312,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"緬甸軍政府宣佈選舉結果無效，觸發全國大規模示威！","createTime":"2021-02-26T12:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T13:08:39.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"430b5f12fcb9a9291a9f6eb8fca355c3cf023b41","tid":2424312,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"緬甸軍政府任命的選舉委員會主席吴丁梭今早（26 日）宣佈，去年 11 月的議會選舉結果無效，再激起緬甸反政變示威者的憤怒。示威者於全國各地聚集示威，而軍政府亦繼續以暴力鎮壓持示威者。<br />\n<br />\n今早在該國最大城市仰光的示威遊行中，防暴警察在仰光大學附近，多次向天開槍驅散附近示威者，但暫時未知是使用實彈，還是橡膠子彈。緬甸警方曾在仰光拘捕一名日本攝影記者，消息亦已由日本大使館確認。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-%E8%BB%8D%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%84%A1%E6%95%88-%E5%86%8D%E8%A7%B8%E7%99%BC%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%91%E5%A4%A9%E9%B3%B4%E6%A7%8D/?fbclid=IwAR2aqrXamb30l78ABPUS7K-754dFg5L4AXtGPFodKmYAZAc8OBc4sFdJ28o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25AE%258A-%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2588-%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E6%25A7%258D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2aqrXamb30l78ABPUS7K-754dFg5L4AXtGPFodKmYAZAc8OBc4sFdJ28o&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2BzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=4b5c17e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25AE%258A-%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25B